679
01:58:03,159 --> 01:58:05,083
Apressem-se!

680
01:59:02,242 --> 01:59:03,620
<i>Coronel?</i>

681
01:59:45,653 --> 01:59:48,807
Asno, lançador de granada!

682
02:00:45,630 --> 02:00:48,802
